1. Clone from git:
    git clone https://gitlab.com/Tsesterh/ns3.git

2. Install packages:
    sudo apt-get install < packages.txt

3. Configure the ns3:
    python 2.7 ./waf configure --enable-examples --disable-tests

4. Run the energy simulation:
    python2.7 ./waf --run scratch/lr-wpan-contiki-energy ->may take a while when running the first time.
